    <header class="comment--meta">
      <div class="vcard"><cite class="comment-author fn"><a href="https://www.blogger.com/profile/05817049547134774699" class="url" rel="ugc external nofollow">Pille</a></cite></div>
      <a href="index.html?p=1478#comment-5919"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2007-05-11T06:04:00-04:00">Friday, May 11, 2007 at 6:04 am</time></a>    </header>

    
    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Oh, and I thought you&#8217;re about to give us another fantastic bouchon recipe (as in &#8216;bouchon au thon&#8217;). Next time in France, I&#8217;ll make sure to visit one of these places!</p>
    </div>

